graph LR
    subgraph Client["🌐 Client"]
        User["Client\n(App)"]
    end

    subgraph Gateway["🚪 API Gateway"]
        AG["ApiGateway\n(YARP)"]
    end

    subgraph APIs["📦 API Services"]
        CA["Catalog.API"]
        BA["Booking.API"]
    end

    subgraph Repo["📚 Catalog Repository"]
        ICR["ICatalogRepository"]
        CR["CatalogRepository"]
    end

    subgraph Workers["⚙️ Background Workers"]
        PW["PaymentProcessor.Worker"]
        ORW["OutboxRelayWorker"]
        CS["CatalogSyncWorker"]
    end

    subgraph Storage["🏗️ Infrastructure"]
        MongoDB["MongoDB"]
        Redis["Redis"]
        RabbitMQ["RabbitMQ"]
        SqlServer["SQL Server"]
    end

    subgraph Models["📋 Data Models"]
        CI["CatalogItem"]
        TO["TicketOrder"]
        OM["OutboxMessage"]
    end

    Seq["Seq\nLogging"]
    Downstream["Downstream Services\n(not shown)"]
    Summary["Summary:
• Gateway routes calls to Catalog.API or Booking.API.
• Booking.API locks seats and emits booking events to queue ticket_orders.
• PaymentProcessor.Worker consumes ticket_orders, writes TicketOrder + OutboxMessage to SQL Server.
• OutboxRelayWorker polls unprocessed OutboxMessage rows and publishes events to exchange ticket_events.
• Catalog.API’s CatalogSyncWorker binds a queue to ticket_events and consumes the integration event.
• After publish, downstream subscribers can also consume the event."]

    User -->|HTTP request| AG
    AG -->|routes to| CA
    AG -->|routes to| BA

    CA -->|calls repository| ICR
    ICR -->|implements| CR
    CR -->|reads| MongoDB

    BA -->|locks seat| Redis
    BA -->|publishes booking event to queue ticket_orders| RabbitMQ

    RabbitMQ -->|ticket_orders consumed by| PW
    PW -->|writes TicketOrder + OutboxMessage| SqlServer
    PW -->|creates| TO
    PW -->|creates| OM

    ORW -->|polls unprocessed OutboxMessage rows| SqlServer
    ORW -->|publishes integration event to exchange ticket_events| RabbitMQ
    RabbitMQ -->|ticket_events consumed by| CS
    CS -->|updates catalog view| MongoDB
    RabbitMQ -.->|fanout event to subscribers| Downstream

    CA -.->|logs| Seq
    BA -.->|logs| Seq
    PW -.->|logs| Seq
    ORW -.->|logs| Seq

    Summary -.-> AG
    Summary -.-> BA
    Summary -.-> PW
    Summary -.-> ORW
    Summary -.-> CA
    Summary -.-> MongoDB
    Summary -.-> SqlServer

